# register scan

Reg number is the register address being checked. Reg 0 is 0x00. Reg 1 is 0x01.

0b00110011 is ID value usually

0b00000111 is PAD_CTRL

0b00010100 is PMU_CMD_AGGR_SET

01110000 is PMU_CMD_AXIS_EN
